Hello Everyone!
This is one of the best scenes from the Marineford war !
Blackbeard after taking Whitebeards devil fruit shows off and planning to sink the marineford island , unfortunately for Him Sengoku and Garp stepped up and stopped him from doing so.
Not only that but Sengoku was giving Blackbeard a pretty hard time.
Hope you guys enjoy!!!!
